9bb3ec1a5f5d0c7adf54f7239f3b9a55","tid":358713,"uid":104406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而想問本身唔做運動 食野又唔節制<br />\n咁就177 62kg<br />\n做番帶氧兩三個月變左60kg正唔正常</blockquote><br />\n你力威字頭 應該問返胡師父"},{"pid":"f844402ce2b5a7948f8b3d74bce07b91e17e6e79","tid":358713,"uid":8751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反而想問本身唔做運動 食野又唔節制<br />\n咁就177 62kg<br />\n做番帶氧兩三個月變左60kg正唔正常</blockquote><br />\n你力威字頭 應該問返胡師父</blockquote><br />\n我做保健架炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd76d425fa60949caa50e072a028b4ced0b930dc","tid":358713,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:56:51.000Z","msg":"睇咩情況架咋,你食唔夠都會唔夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f047868e96606ed4b62e72e419de981afbddb9f","tid":358713,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:58:29.000Z","msg":"我feel到我手臂肌肉實左，腹部扁左"},{"pid":"85981489325ae79dfaf6ec19a807a4f9b068f255","tid":358713,"uid":104406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:59:08.000Z","msg":"其實樓主係講體重定其他？<br />\n我見人人都講到好似做既重量輕左"},{"pid":"e0dbc3ed01e1969a40258ff8b3ecf878240bb970","tid":358713,"uid":8751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我feel到我手臂肌肉實左，腹部扁左</blockquote><br />\n有冇機會係你d肉撕裂唔夠<br />\n又無操後protein 所以無乜增長<br />\n但又因為你做gym整走左脂肪所以變到咁"},{"pid":"ac9f8db4afa648717d20d4391e154c801ecb7af2","tid":358713,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我feel到我手臂肌肉實左，腹部扁左</blockquote><br />\n有冇機會係你d肉撕裂唔夠<br />\n又無操後protein 所以無乜增長<br />\n但又因為你做gym整走左脂肪所以變到咁</blockquote><br />\n操後食咩最好"},{"pid":"d6a040d60363fe2ad4a0887bb05e991f1bc76df1","tid":358713,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我feel到我手臂肌肉實左，腹部扁左</blockquote><br />\n有冇機會係你d肉撕裂唔夠<br />\n又無操後protein 所以無乜增長<br />\n但又因為你做gym整走左脂肪所以變到咁</blockquote><br />\n應該係"},{"pid":"83de28cc3333f0a7911c2f3dc13e44635e150967","tid":358713,"uid":104406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我feel到我手臂肌肉實左，腹部扁左</blockquote><br />\n正常初入門 重訓加帶氧都會輕左先<br />\n因為你消緊脂 加上 肌肉生長係好難(除非你飲奶粉)<br />\n到你體脂去到好低 而你又開始體重上返<br />\n恭喜你 你成功了"},{"pid":"ef1fa2e1f806e664a1462828c2e8a84709e6998c","tid":358713,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:03:19.000Z","msg":"其實本身日日都食唔少肉"},{"pid":"7a1dcf9441e6a1ab4faa34cc5ca955835126d0da","tid":358713,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我feel到我手臂肌肉實左，腹部扁左</blockquote><br />\n正常初入門 重訓加帶氧都會輕左先<br />\n因為你消緊脂 加上 肌肉生長係好難(除非你飲奶粉)<br />\n到你體脂去到好低 而你又開始體重上返<br />\n恭喜你 你成功了</blockquote><br />\n謝謝，前排游水又做gym次數好癲下，係今個星期冇游"},{"pid":"dc8156a75ba873ba4cfe5915a61a038f9f77c040","tid":358713,"uid":8751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我feel到我手臂肌肉實左，腹部扁左</blockquote><br />\n有冇機會係你d肉撕裂唔夠<br />\n又無操後protein 所以無乜增長<br />\n但又因為你做gym整走左脂肪所以變到咁</blockquote><br />\n應該係</blockquote><br />\n之前玩開street workout無控制過飲食<br />\n我對你呢種正規健身無乜認識<br />\n但不嬲大多數都食小d碳水化合物<br />\n食小d飯 （因為殿粉到最尾會變糖）<br />\n食多d肉 同時食多d菜<br />\n我唔知有冇錯 有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0486eb5fe81a93acd5f71576b3cafbc8597dd3f","tid":358713,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:04:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我feel到我手臂肌肉實左，腹部扁左</blockquote><br />\n正常初入門 重訓加帶氧都會輕左先<br />\n因為你消緊脂 加上 肌肉生長係好難(除非你飲奶粉)<br />\n到你體脂去到好低 而你又開始體重上返<br />\n恭喜你 你成功了</blockquote><br />\n謝謝，前排游水又做gym次數好癲下，係今個星期冇游</blockquote><br />\n但就日日做gym,1-1.5hrs"},{"pid":"343c0c07d348ce758ebc5ca013676f869fed2682","tid":358713,"uid":104406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實本身日日都食唔少肉</blockquote><br />\n澱粉類都要有"},{"pid":"beebc10b86332b73949aa0354d1d26fdedfd8e1c","tid":358713,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實本身日日都食唔少肉</blockquote><br />\n澱粉類都要有</blockquote><br />\n午餐晚餐都食好多飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日都好餓咁"},{"pid":"91b92ec1183aa9e0e94385fe2def7e88f459c67c","tid":358713,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:05:43.000Z","msg":"做gym一個月, 日日多肉少飯少汁, 80kg-&gt;75kg<br />\n本身肥底我估係正常 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5f910acdeff09e6d08421c287fc2334a98fc53","tid":358713,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:05:48.000Z","msg":"但又驚食得多肉又肥返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a317a36284ecb8459ce4db32e62f1fcda714d67a","tid":358713,"uid":8751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:06:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但又驚食得多肉又肥返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔食皮既話 佢肉裡邊既脂肪含量相對小d"},{"pid":"e950e54ca08d77f898c7b3b458fa065b7def9c2a","tid":358713,"uid":104406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但又驚食得多肉又肥返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本上戒糖戒煎炸野 好難會肥返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1a372a8fc4130ca6b865432aae343a0aeb2259","tid":358713,"uid":70688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:26:03.000Z","msg":"食野唔少姐係幾多呀，想重就1日食2500卡啦"},{"pid":"4a5a0944f